User - Class in models
USER CLASS
A User object will contain User ID Name Password Email Type of User
A User object can be one of the types below: User Student Career Center Staff Company Representative Other than the default type (User), every other User type will also include their own specific fields.

ALL Users will have access to basic user management features, including login, logout and change password.
User - Enum constant in enum class models.User.TypesOfUser
 
User(String, String, String) - Constructor for class models.User
Class Constructor
User.TypesOfUser - Enum Class in models
Enum that contains different user account types - User, Student, CareerCenterStaff, CompanyRepresentative
User objects of type "Student" and "Career Center Staff" are automatically assigned their respective types from the sample excel file.

The default type "User" is initiated first, as in the case of "Company Representative" they must be approved by a user
that is a "Career Center Staffs" type first, before officially becoming a "Company Representative".
